# Skelenest Project

Read the canonical project skill at `SKILL.md` in the repository root, then follow it for all work in this project.

## Quick Trigger Guidance

Use this skill for:

- NestJS module, controller, provider, service, DTO, guard, strategy, or test changes.
- Persistence changes for the selected ORM.
- Auth/session/token changes when the auth starter module is selected.
- Redis, BullMQ, throttler, Swagger, Docker, or environment configuration changes.
- Reviews that need to detect unselected technology leakage.

## Core Rule

The selected stack is the contract. Add only the technologies selected in the generated project unless the user explicitly asks to change the stack.
